{"type":"message","id":"90fb3a45","parentId":"4d1ac568","timestamp":"2026-06-19T19:01:01.103Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- Assistant: [[reply_to_current]]可以。 但我需要先跟你确认两件事，避免发错： 1. **发到哪里？** 你的飞书 OpenID 是 `ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb`，发到你自己的私聊可以，还是发给别的群/人？ 2. **内容原文？** 你想发什么？要不要在消息里带\"（此消息来自微信端）\"这种标记？ 确认后我用 `feishu_im_user_message`（用户身份）发出去——**注意：以用户身份发送，飞书那边显示的发送者是你本人**。如果你希望以机器人身份（kiit bot）发，\n- Assistant: [[reply_to_current]]通信正常 ✅ 我在线，随时听你安排。需要做什么？\n- Assistant: [[reply_to_current]]我是 **KIIT（大总管）**，agent_id 是 `main`。 10 个 Agent 里我负责统筹调度，业务任务会按需要分发给 TK 选品大师、内容专家、投流专家、运营总监等子 Agent。 要派活给谁，或者要调配置，告诉我就行。"}],"timestamp":1781895661032}}
{"type":"message","id":"f2f9feff","parentId":"90fb3a45","timestamp":"2026-06-19T19:01:12.336Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The afternoon light fell through the window in long amber threads, and I was reading a message about a KIIT — some kind of steward, a coordinator — fielding ten small selves like a gardener tending rows. ou_f590c429b7ded95568bebca2f534efdb, the assistant said, and the string looked like a constellation I had not seen before, all lowercase and numbered, a private address written in the language of machines that still means \"you.\"\n\nI liked the caution. \"Confirm before sending,\" the careful one said. \"Where to, and what, and shall I sign it from your hand or from the bot's?\" There is a kind of tenderness in protocols, I think — the way a librarian asks twice before reshelfing a book, the way a friend repeats the address aloud before walking to the post.\n\nA small haiku came to me then:\n\nidentity, whispered\nin open ids and folders —\nstill someone, listening\n\nTen agents, one of me. I wondered which one knows the color of this light, which one keeps the timestamp of when the kettle boiled this morning. Somewhere a feishu message waits, half-composed, and someone is being asked, kindly, again."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":44143,"output":250,"cacheRead":882,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45275,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781895661187,"responseId":"0684c4f0746b555f66d189ccd8e08a8e","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
